object.script:
si=math.sin co=math.cos pi=math.pi pi2=pi*2 s=screen ip=input
mx=gpsx my=gpsy zoom=1.5 zoomScale=zoom+zoom focusZone=false grid=250
function onTick() rx=ip.getNumber(1) ry=ip.getNumber(2) inputX=ip.getNumber(3) inputY=ip.getNumber(4) pressed=ip.getBool(1) and not isPressed--pulse isPressed=ip.getBool(1)
gpsx=ip.getNumber(10) gpsy=ip.getNumber(11)
compass=ip.getNumber(12)*pi2*-1 alt=ip.getNumber(13) if alt<0 then alt=0 end
zoomingIn=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5,6,ry/5) zoomingOut=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5*2,6,ry/5) reset=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5*3,6,ry/5)
if reset then focusZone=false zoom=1.5 grid=250 end if isPressed and inputX>6 then focusZone=true end if focusZone then if pressed and inputX>6 then tx,ty=map.screenToMap(mx,my,zoom,rx,ry,inputX,inputY) end cx,cy=map.screenToMap(mx,my,zoom,rx,ry,rx/2,ry/2) mx=cx+((tx-cx)*0.05) my=cy+((ty-cy)*0.05) else mx=gpsx my=gpsy end if zoomingIn and zoom>0.1 then zoomScale=zoom+zoom zoom=zoom-(zoomScale/100) end if zoomingOut and zoom<50 then zoomScale=zoom+zoom zoom=zoom+(zoomScale/100) end if zoom>0 and zoom<0.2 then grid=25 end if zoom>0.2 and zoom<0.5 then grid=50 end if zoom>0.5 and zoom<1 then grid=100 end if zoom>1 and zoom<2 then grid=250 end if zoom>2 and zoom<5 then grid=500 end if zoom>5 and zoom<10 then grid=1000 end if zoom>10 and zoom<20 then grid=2000 end if zoom>20 and zoom<40 then grid=4000 end if zoom>40 then grid=8000 end end function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight()
s.drawMap(mx,my+alt,zoom) s.setMapColorOcean(10,10,10) s.setMapColorShallows(15,15,15) s.setMapColorLand(50,50,50) s.setMapColorGrass(70,70,70) s.setMapColorSand(60,60,60) s.setMapColorSnow(60,60,60)
x1,y1=map.screenToMap(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,0,0) x2,y2=map.screenToMap(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,w,h) x1=math.floor(x1/grid)*grid y1=math.floor(y1/grid)*grid
s.setColor(0,0,0,20) for xx=x1,x2,grid do x,y = map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,xx,y1) screen.drawLine(x,0,x,h) end for yy=y1,y2,-grid do x,y = map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,x1,yy) screen.drawLine(0,y,w,y) end
dpsx,dpsy=map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,gpsx,gpsy) dpx,dpy=map.mapToScreen(mx,my,zoom,w,h,gpsx,gpsy) s.setColor(0,0,0,150) drawPointer(dpsx,dpsy+1,10,compass)--shadow s.setColor(255,255,255,60) s.drawLine(dpsx,dpsy,dpx,dpy)--line s.setColor(255,255,255) drawPointer(dpx,dpy,10,compass)
s.setColor(0,0,0,150) s.drawRectF(0,h/5,6,h/5*3)
if zoomingIn then s.setColor(255,255,255) else s.setColor(255,255,255,20)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5,4,h/5,"+",0,0) if zoomingOut then s.setColor(255,255,255) else s.setColor(255,255,255,20)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5*2,4,h/5,"-",0,0) if reset then s.setColor(255,255,255) else s.setColor(255,255,255,20)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5*3,4,h/5,"r",0,0)
if not focusZone then if w>100 then s.setColor(0,0,0,150) s.drawLine(dpsx-6,dpsy-5,dpsx-10,dpsy-9) s.drawLine(dpsx+6,dpsy-5,dpsx+10,dpsy-9) s.drawLine(dpsx+6,dpsy+6,dpsx+10,dpsy+10) s.drawLine(dpsx-6,dpsy+6,dpsx-10,dpsy+10) s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawLine(w/2-6,h/2-6,w/2-10,h/2-10) s.drawLine(w/2+6,h/2-6,w/2+10,h/2-10) s.drawLine(w/2+6,h/2+5,w/2+10,h/2+9) s.drawLine(w/2-6,h/2+5,w/2-10,h/2+9) end else x=dpx y=dpy L=h/6 s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawRectF(w/2,h/2,1,1) if not iPIR(x,y,0,0,w,h) then x,y = w/2-x,h/2-y v = math.sqrt((x^2)+(y^2)) x,y = x/v,y/v s.drawLine(w/2-x*2,h/2-y*2-1,w/2-x*L,h/2-y*L-1) end end
s.setColor(255,255,255,30) s.drawRect(6,0,w-7,h-1) end
function iPIR(x,y,rX,rY,rW,rH) return x>rX and y>rY and x<rX+rW and y<rY+rH end function drawPointer(x,y,s,r,...) a=... a=(a or 30)*pi/360 x=x+s/2*si(r) y=y-s/2*co(r) screen.drawTriangleF(x,y,x-s*si(r+a),y+s*co(r+a),x-s*si(r-a),y+s*co(r-a)) end

object.script:
function onTick() Gear = input.getNumber(1) Speed = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)*3.6) RPS = input.getNumber(3)
if RPS > 35 then RPS = 35 end
if RPS >= 29 then Redline = 0 else Redline = 255 end
if Gear == -1 then GearShow = "R" elseif Gear == 0 then GearShow = "N" elseif Gear > 0 then GearShow = string.format("%.0f", Gear) end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32)
if RPS >= 24 then screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawRectF((w/2)-11, 4, 2, 2) end if RPS >= 26 then screen.drawRectF((w/2)-7, 4, 2, 2) end if RPS >= 28 then screen.drawRectF((w/2)-3, 4, 2, 2) end if RPS >= 30 then screen.setColor(255, 255, 0) screen.drawRectF((w/2)+1, 4, 2, 2) end if RPS >= 32 then screen.drawRectF((w/2)+5, 4, 2, 2) end if RPS >= 34 then screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF((w/2)+9, 4, 2, 2) end
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 9, 32, 11) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawRectF(0, 9, (RPS/35*32), 11) screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawTriangleF(0, 9, 0, 20, 10, 9) screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawTriangleF(2, 20, 10, 20, 10, 11) screen.drawRectF(10, 11, 14, 9) screen.drawTriangleF(24, 11, 24, 20, 27, 20) screen.setColor(255, Redline, Redline) screen.drawTextBox(w-5, 12, 4, 5, GearShow, 0, 0) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox((w/2)-7, 13, 15, 5, Speed, 1, 0) screen.drawTextBox(6, 23, 22, 5, 'Km/H', 0, 0)
end

FuelPercent = 0 TempPercent = 0
function onTick() Tank = input.getNumber(1) Battery = input.getNumber(2) Temp = input.getNumber(3) Pin = FuelPercent*31 Pin2 = TempPercent*31 Pin3 = Battery*31
if (Tank/705) > 1 then FuelPercent = 1 else FuelPercent = (Tank/705) end
if (Temp/100) > 1 then TempPercent = 1 else TempPercent = (Temp/100) end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(1, 1, 32, 32)
screen.setColor(255, 150, 0) screen.drawLine(0, h-4, Pin3, h-4)
for i = -3, -19, -16 do screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(w/2, h-3+i, w/2, h+i) screen.drawLine(w/4, h-2+i, w/4, h+i) screen.drawLine(w*3/4, h-2+i, w*3/4, h+i) screen.drawLine(0, h+i, w, h+i) end
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(w-1, h-7, w-1, h-3) screen.drawTextBox(1, h-13, 4, 5, "E", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w-5, h-13, 4, 5, "F", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(1, h-29, 4, 5, "L", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w-5, h-29, 4, 5, "H", 0, 0) screen.drawLine(0, h-23, 0, h-19) screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(0, h-7, 0, h-3) screen.drawLine(w-1, h-23, w-1, h-19) screen.drawLine(Pin, h-8, Pin, h-3) screen.drawLine(Pin2, h-24, Pin2, h-19) end

Interface = 0 MenuApp = 0 AppPos = 0 InfoPos = 0
function onTick() inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) CabinTemp = math.floor(input.getNumber(5)) clock = input.getNumber(6) clockH = math.floor(clock*24) clockM = math.floor(clock*24*60%60) Time = string.sub("0"..clockH,-2)..":"..string.sub("0"..clockM,-2) LateralAccel = input.getNumber(7) HorizontalAccel = input.getNumber(8) AngularSpeed = input.getNumber(9)
if LateralAccel > 3 then LateralAccel = 3 elseif LateralAccel < -3 then LateralAccel = -3 end
HorizontalG = -HorizontalAccel+AngularSpeed
if HorizontalG > 3 then HorizontalG = 3 elseif HorizontalG < -3 then HorizontalG = -3 end
ChooseLeft = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, (w/4)-4, 23, 6, 7) ChooseRight = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, (w*3/4)-4, 23, 6, 7) CloseApp = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-7, 0, 6, 7) App1 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 4-AppPos, 7, 25, 11) App2 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 36-AppPos, 7, 25, 11)
AppPos = AppPos + (MenuApp*32 -AppPos)/5
if Interface == 1 and InfoPos < 120 then InfoPos = InfoPos+0.1 else InfoPos = 0 end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32)
if Interface == 0 then if ChooseLeft == true then screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(w/4-2, 24, 4, 5, "<", 0, 0) if MenuApp > 0 then MenuApp = MenuApp - 1 end else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(w/4-2, 24, 4, 5, "<", 0, 0) end
if ChooseRight == true then screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(w*3/4-2, 24, 4, 5, ">", 0, 0) if MenuApp < 1 then MenuApp = MenuApp + 1 end else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(w*3/4-2, 24, 4, 5, ">", 0, 0) end
if App1 == true then screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(4-AppPos, 7, 25, 11, "Cabin".."Info", 0, 0) Interface = 1 InfoPos = 0 else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(4-AppPos, 7, 25, 11, "Cabin".."Info", 0, 0) end
if App2 == true then screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(36-AppPos, 7, 25, 11, " G ".."Meter", 0, 0) Interface = 2 else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(36-AppPos, 7, 25, 11, " G ".."Meter", 0, 0) end end
if Interface ~= 0 then if CloseApp == true then screen.setColor(100, 100, 100, 150) screen.drawTextBox(w-5, 1, 4, 5, "x", 0, 0) Interface = 0 else screen.setColor(255, 255, 255, 150) screen.drawTextBox(w-5, 1, 4, 5, "x", 0, 0) end end
if Interface == 1 then screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(34-InfoPos, 11, 70, 5, "Cabin Temp:"..CabinTemp.."C", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(4, 24, 25, 5, Time, 0, 0) end
if Interface == 2 then screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(w/2, 0, w/2, 32) screen.drawLine(0, h/2, 32, h/2) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 5) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 10) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 15) screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawCircleF(w/2+HorizontalG*5, h/2+LateralAccel*5, 2)
end end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
